snippet.title: EVERSPACE 2 | Leviathan Deep Dive
snippet.description:
EVERSPACE 2: Titans brings two new storylines to EVERSPACE 2 this fall. 

Today we deep dive into what's to come in the Leviathan storyline for EVERSPACE 2 pilots in our upcoming DLC. Seek out the truth of mysterious creatures thought extinct and prepare to dive deep inside. 

EVERSPACE 2: Titans launches September 16, 2024 on Steam, GOG, Xbox, and PlayStation.

Wishlist now on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2873460/EVERSPACE_2__Titans/

Follow development on:
